OL,3,C'He's scared of his party': Starmer
OL,4,Ccalls on PM to return cash from Tory
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,FITV News Political Correspondent Harry
OL,8,FHorton and Political Reporter Jasmine
OL,9,FCameron-Chileshe report.
OL,11,FSir Keir Starmer has called on Rishi
OL,12,FSunak to return party donations from
OL,13,FFrank Hester, after he made "racist"
OL,14,Fremarks about MP Diane Abbott.
OL,16,FTory donor Frank Hester is alleged to
OL,17,Fhave said in 2019 that Ms Abbott,
OL,18,FBritain's longest-serving black MP,
OL,19,Fmade him "want to hate all black
OL,20,Fwomen" and that she "should be shot".
