OL,7,FMs Abbott has expressed frustration on
OL,8,FX that she wasn't chosen by the
OL,9,FSpeaker to ask a question at PMQs.
OL,11,FShe tweeted, "I don't know whose
OL,12,Finterests the Speaker thinks he is
OL,13,Fserving. But it is not the interests
OL,14,Fof the Commons or democracy."
OL,16,FA spokeswoman for Speaker Sir Lindsay
OL,17,FHoyle said there was "not enough time"
OL,18,Fto call all MPs to ask a question,
OL,19,Fincluding Diane Abbott.
