OL,7,FIn a U-turn on Tuesday, Mr Sunak
OL,8,Fdescribed Mr Hester's remarks as
OL,9,F"racist and wrong" in a statement,
OL,10,Fafter Number 10 had initially refused
OL,11,Fto do so.
OL,13,FThe Scottish Conservatives called on
OL,14,Fthe government to "carefully review
OL,15,Fthe donations it has received from
OL,16,FHester in response to his remarks",
OL,17,Fand confirmed the Scottish
OL,18,FConservative Party had never accepted
OL,19,Fdonations from Mr Hester.
