OL,4,Ccalls on PM to return cash from Tory
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,FLabour MP Marsha de Cordova asked the
OL,8,Fprime minister if he would return a
OL,9,F#15,000 from Hester to cover the cost
OL,10,Fof a helicopter flights, but Mr Sunak
OL,11,Freplied "no", instead insisting he is
OL,12,F"pleased that the gentleman is
OL,13,Fsupporting a party that represents one
OL,14,Fof the most diverse governments in
OL,15,Fthis country's history."
OL,17,FMs de Cordova said it was "shameful"
OL,18,Fthat it took Mr Sunak more than 24
OL,19,Fhours to label Mr Hester's comments
OL,20,F"racist".
