OL,7,FWhen asked on Wednesday if he would
OL,8,Faccept more donations from Mr Hester,
OL,9,FPostal Minister Kevin Hollinrake said
OL,10,F"that's not a decision for me to
OL,11,Ftake", but that "if somebody
OL,12,Fapologises for something they've done
OL,13,Fwrong, I don't think we should judge
OL,14,Ftheir character adversely on that
OL,15,Fbasis."
OL,17,FHe insisted Mr Hester "has apologised
OL,18,Ffor what he said", and that "you can
OL,19,Finterpret what he said in different
OL,20,Fways".
