OL,7,F"To connect somebody's character with
OL,8,Ftheir skin colour is absolutely the
OL,9,Fwrong thing to do", he said.
OL,11,FIn a sign of Tory divisions over the
OL,12,Fissue, Conservative West Midlands
OL,13,FMayor Andy Street said he would return
